        class="h-auto w-full rounded-sm md:rounded-md"
        src={Ad1}
        alt="An ad featuring a person holding a quilt around them. The text reads My style is Fresh.Bright.Fun. And made by me."
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="my-[45px] flex flex-row items-center gap-[10px] px-[20px] md:my-[120px] md:gap-[40px] md:px-[60px]">
    <div class="w-1/3">
      <Image
        class="w-full rounded-md md:rounded-lg"
        src={MultiCat}
        alt="An assortment of arts and crafts tools and supplies laid out around a framed painting."
      />
    </div>
    <div class="w-1/3">
      <Image class="w-full rounded-md md:rounded-lg" src={Cake} alt="A spinning cake with lit candles." />
    </div>
    <div class="w-1/3">
      <Image class="w-full rounded-md md:rounded-lg" src={Fox1} alt="Two children wearing knitted fox hats." />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="karla mx-auto my-[45px] max-w-[950px] px-[25px] md:my-[120px] md:columns-2 md:gap-[80px]">
    <h1 class="mb-[40px] text-[24px] font-[700] text-[#363131]">Brand Pillars</h1>
    <h2 class="font-[700] tracking-widest text-[#CF3538]">WE RESPECT YOUR TIME</h2>
    <p class="mb-[40px] text-[#363131] md:pr-[20px]">
      We help you cut through the startup hassle by curating everything you need in one place and meeting you on your
      favorite platform. From project kits designed for your skill level to step-by-step guidance, you can be assured
      that you’ll make something great here.
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-[700] tracking-widest text-[#CF3538]">WE'VE BEEN THERE</h2>
    <p class="mb-[40px] text-[#363131] md:pr-[20px]">
      We anticipate all the hills and valleys because we’ve gone through them too. At every turn, it feels like there’s
      a real person helping you avoid common mistakes and setting you up for success.
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-[700] tracking-widest text-[#CF3538]">WE'RE FOR EVERY MAKER</h2>
    <p class="mb-[40px] text-[#363131]">
      Whether you’re a never-crafted newbie or an accomplished maker with decades of experience, we help you discover
      the best options for you and grow your skills.
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-[700] tracking-widest text-[#CF3538]">WE KEEP IT FRESH</h2>
    <p class="mb-[40px] text-[#363131]">
      We’re that endlessly creative friend who’s always in the know about the next incredible thing, from trends and
      techniques to tools and tips. There’s always something new to see and try.
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-[700] tracking-widest text-[#CF3538]">WE BELIEVE IN THE JOY OF CREATIVITY</h2>
    <p class="mb-[40px] text-[#363131]">
      You love making. We get it because we feel the same way. We understand one of the greatest sources of happiness is
      the creative world we build.
    </p>
